  "title": "Perm Staff Nurse - Plastic Surgery, Up to $4.2K #HKH",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist surgeon in OT procedures for plastic & aesthetic surgeries  </li><li>Maintain sterile field and ensure compliance with surgical protocols  </li><li>Prepare surgical instruments and consumables  </li><li>Support post-operative patient care and recovery  </li><li>Handle documentation and inventory of OT supplies.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Nursing</li><li>Min 1 to 2 years of any nursing experience </li></ul><p><strong>Up to $4.2K </strong></p><p><strong>5.5 Days Office Hours</strong></p><p></p><p>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to <strong>kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
